OOC: Unitron, Your bots are at the CF now, right? If not the maximal part of 
this post is void. Teltoli, 2 missles are the minimum.  Just so you know and 
wont fire three again.

:::Orion/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky Lynx/Jetstorm/Sharpedge/Godfather/Gigatron:::

::Orion fires 2 missles at Dark One.  Ratchet fires 8 shots from each of his 
2 blasters at Sixshot.  Sideswipe fires 25 shots at Injector and 2 missles at 
Bumblebee. Sky Lynx fires 2 missles from each of his missle launcher at 
Manterror.  Sharpedge and Jetstorm get hit by Caitiff's attacks, but they 
dodge the EMP stuff.  Sharpedge gets hit by Hot Rods optic blasts, but 
Jetstorm only gets hit by one charge.  Hellbat gets hit by the EMPs.  Hellbat 
fires 2 missles at the autoguns.  Sharpedge fires 1 missle at Hot Rod and 1 
at Caitiff.  Jetstorm fires 12 energy blasts at Caitiff, 13 energy blasts at 
Hot Rod and 25 rapid fire optic blasts at the autoguns.  Godfather gets hit 
by 1 of the missles and dodges the poison dart.  he fires 8 more shots from 
his pistol at Teltoli::
Godfather: Whack for my daddy-o!
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
::Gigatron cannot stop himself from crying from the amazing things before 
him.  He looks to the others::
Gigatron: w-what d-do we do now?

--part1_a6.d552446.27698e93_boundary
